data.description: A must see riverfront community with glorious views of the trees and river from all balconies! This 3-story end unit offers you an opportunity to create your dream home! UPDATED WATER HEATER/AC(2020), CARPET(2019). The first floor contains the first bedroom with a patio, laundry room with WASHER/DRYER(2020) INCLUDED, a full bathroom, and access to the attached 1-car garage. The second floor features the kitchen, half bath, living room, dining room, and balcony. On the third floor you'll find the owner's suite with two walk-in closets, en-suite bathroom, and a private balcony. Additionally, here lies the third bedroom with another full bath. Minutes to Downtown Melbourne, the airport, and a short drive to local beaches and parks. Come experience fine Florida living!
